p:
The Gene Ontology (GO)
64 and ReactomePA
65 were used to determine enrichment of biological processes and pathways, respectively on DEGs. We used the ClusterProfiler package from R
66 for ReactomePA generation and GO enrichment by over-representation test. The enrichment was generated with Benjamini & Hochberg (BH) adjusted p-value method with a p-value cutoff of 0.01.
